OL,3,CWater supplier's profit doubles as
OL,4,Ccustomers see bill hikes
OL,6,FA water firm's profit more than
OL,7,Fdoubled in 2024 before it hit
OL,8,Fcustomers with a steep rise in bills
OL,9,Fin April.
OL,11,FUnited Utilities' more than seven
OL,12,Fmillion customers across the North
OL,13,FWest are seeing their water bills rise
OL,14,Fby an average of 32% over the next
OL,15,Ffive years.
OL,17,FBut the biggest annual rise came in
OL,18,FApril this year, when bills surged by
OL,19,Fan average of #86 for a typical
OL,20,Fhousehold.
