OL,3,CWater supplier's profit doubles as
OL,4,Ccustomers see bill hikes
OL,6,FThe increase is designed to fund #13.7
OL,7,Fbillion of upgrades to its pipes and
OL,8,Fsewers, after the company was accused
OL,9,Fof illegally pumping raw sewage into
OL,10,FLake Windermere in recent years.
OL,12,FBut for the year ending 31 March, as
OL,13,Fit geared up to charge customers more,
OL,14,FUnited Utilities' pre-tax profits also
OL,15,Fmore than doubled to #355 million.
OL,17,FAnd it said on Thursday that it will
OL,18,Fincrease its dividend payout to
OL,19,Finvestors by 4.2% to 34.6p.
