OL,3,CWater supplier's profit doubles as
OL,4,Ccustomers see bill hikes
OL,6,FChief executive Louise Beardmore said:
OL,7,F"We have delivered another strong set
OL,8,Fof results for customers, communities
OL,9,Fand the environment in the North West."
OL,11,FShe pointed to the company cutting
OL,12,Fsewage spills per storm overflow by a
OL,13,Fquarter last year.
OL,15,FThe company was recently accused of
OL,16,Ffailing to report more than 100
OL,17,Fmillion litres of untreated sewage
OL,18,Fthat it illegally dumped into
OL,19,FWindermere over a three-year period.
