OL,3,CWater supplier's profit doubles as
OL,4,Ccustomers see bill hikes
OL,6,FMs Beardmore told MPs in February that
OL,7,FUnited Utilities' record on spills and
OL,8,Fflooding "isn't good enough".
OL,10,FShe took home a pay packet of #1.4
OL,11,Fmillion last year, made up of a base
OL,12,Fsalary worth #690,000, plus benefits,
OL,13,Fbonuses and long-term share awards.
OL,15,FThe UK's privatised water companies
OL,16,Fhave faced growing public outrage over
OL,17,Fthe extent of pollution, rising bills,
OL,18,Fhigh dividends, and executive pay and
OL,19,Fbonuses.
