OL,6,FThe results come after a survey
OL,7,Frevealed households' trust in water
OL,8,Fcompanies has fallen to a new low amid
OL,9,Fthe crisis.
OL,11,FFewer households ` 53%, down 2% on
OL,12,Flast year to another all-time low `
OL,13,Fbelieve the amount water companies
OL,14,Fcharge is fair, according to the
OL,15,FConsumer Council for Water's (CCW)
OL,16,Fannual Water Matters study.
